# Software Engineering Standard — Git Ignore
# Repository configuration per Phase 2 (§10, FR-17)

# Editor artifacts
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.vscode/
.idea/

# OS artifacts
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.bak

# Generated artifacts that are reproducible from authoritative sources
# Per §11.1: Generated artifacts MUST be reproducible; they need not be
# committed if they can be regenerated. Uncomment when generation tooling exists.
# standard/dependency-graph.md
# standard/traceability-graph.md
